data.title: California Railroads (California) Scanner Frequencies and Radio Frequency Reference
data.meta_description: Scanner Frequencies and Radio Frequency Reference for California Railroads (California)
data.text:
See also UP Lick Subdivision on 160.74 MHz (AAR42) for Road operations between Tamien and Gilroy Stations, shared with Union Pacific and Coast Starlight.

Yard 1 and Yard 2 channels are used in the San Jose CEMOF, San Francisco Yard and Gilroy Yard.
